{"tid":978963,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE中文] 又係新一年ORAL訓練季節","createTime":"2019-01-12T10:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T13:07:51.000Z","uid":102225,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41f51a07a43fdb151a134d2907f09a0a023df50b","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"成日都聽到有人問我：「我識廣東話佢識廣東話，點解佢攞5**我攞1。」<br />\n<br />\n原因只係因為佢有你冇嘅技巧同例子...<br />\n<br />\n只要你熟HKEAA評分準則，見到攞分位識搶就可以了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/m0eeJPe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fm0eeJPe&h=ca959cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/tRGZjaK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FtRGZjaK&h=5dc36358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒會係度分享下考試心得，我亦都開咗個TG搞match up幫大家出學校同其他同志free fight<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEfDt3QbB0FsEH6ZjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEfDt3QbB0FsEH6ZjQ&d=mOYtx0gTspmDMSj35yKdKROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=79285786\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEfDt3QbB0FsEH6ZjQ</a>"},{"pid":"3e36e1d5c1c698523346ee64dc7200bba3e8fb4f","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VsbE2CA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVsbE2CA.png&h=fd8cc429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fb4fAXB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFb4fAXB.png&h=83f374f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩鳩圖都唔識貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20b7a9f5bf4ee5ca5fd403e0e912a48f6be9048","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"首先我要講解下呢份卷易係邊難係邊<br />\n口試要求嘅野基本上好少，只要意識技巧立論例子齊哂就可以5**<br />\n教咁多年都可以幫人升1-2個grade(Retake)<br />\n但係好多同學Oral，只係不斷操操操(其實多同其他對手對陣都好嘅，知己知彼呀嗎)<br />\n比你操幾百次，知道毛病出係邊度嗎？<br />\n練習嘅時候重點不在說話題目，而係說話能力<br />\n如何當場解題、當場準備、當場應對先係重點"},{"pid":"78224780805379c0a377c9fa4477745437120029","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"中文口試評分準則分為兩種：闡述語言、應對態度<br />\n闡述語言＝內容<br />\n應對態度＝技巧<br />\n所以中文口試基本上係針對呢兩點嚟打就可以<br />\n<br />\n好多時補習社會教大家用咩「共識必殺技」、「總結五式」、「歸納七式」...<br />\n當炙唔係冇用，問題係大家識唔識係咩時間用以上嘅招數<br />\n死背考試硬用，出到嚟一定會係反效果，因為時機錯咗"},{"pid":"61464e326aaa62fb5f95d6bfe9e2ea9938e5f949","tid":978963,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"error<br />\n入唔到"},{"pid":"66b01eeed1fd058bc589df1cdc9386dd5523aa14","tid":978963,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"group入邊得管理員講到野?"},{"pid":"2c1c1f240b83198eb6ba085aeb6a43128c361dc0","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b01eeed1fd058bc589df1cdc9386dd5523aa14","tid":978963,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"group入邊得管理員講到野?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"唔係架，Channel同討論區係兩個gp嚟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ec612d3957f0784dd26e2e6aa2c337bebd75d8","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61464e326aaa62fb5f95d6bfe9e2ea9938e5f949","tid":978963,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"error<br />\n入唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"Me add u lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80b2c135180144b691fd4a9e591d44aef494e67","tid":978963,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/C1M8K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FC1M8K&d=mOYtx0gTspmDMSj35yKdKROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c70e9258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/C1M8K</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eb2ac24c72f73adc72d7bfb996365d26d5dcc7","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"首輪發言<br />\n<br />\n一般補習社會將五個人分為五個位有唔同技巧<br />\n從應對態度去睇<br />\n首輪發言有一樣緊要嘢，就係最後一句<br />\n「唔知下一位同學有啲咩睇法呢？」<br />\n呢句係表示你有討論意識，而非個人朗讀<br />\n提一提下一位同學可以發言啦，畀人哋知道你講完咗<br />\n唔可以由Marker提你完<br />\n展示你對首輪發言有充足既認識<br />\n<br />\n如果其實同考生跟尾狗炒你講嘢，咁你一定有分加<br />\n因為你引導到其他同學討論"},{"pid":"c3bc32924b5cc7f5743dc70856f3b339a60c9730","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"正常係每個人都會講自己立場同提出論證，第二三四五亦會開始對立場唔同。<br />\n<br />\n論證一般要拎高分，一係你比好多例子，一係個例子夠精闢。<br />\n所以技巧分更加必要啦。<br />\n<br />\n回應人地時，除非人地錯得離哂譜，唔係嘅話可以婉轉啲。<br />\n唔好下下話人錯，表示自己係良性討論而唔係有心懷惡意去駁斥人地。"},{"pid":"6844bfa76970fe8ca587cc327a4452e45fe8f0bc","tid":978963,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"講呢啲係咪其實冇人想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}